00:05:10.700 --> 00:05:11.980
Uslu dur.

00:05:11.980 --> 00:05:13.540
Hepsi çok güzel.

00:05:14.140 --> 00:05:15.140
Ne dersin?

00:05:15.140 --> 00:05:16.960
